name: Moucheeser
description:
As I said, your goal is to get to the cheese, then to the mink. The selection of maps is random, but you can change the map or create your own.

Each new map lasts a minute.

The maps are chosen randomly.

Some features of the movement of the mouse character.

Initial controls that can be changed in the game:

F - move to the left

H - move to the right

T - jump
